{"tid":692944,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【荔枝狗肉節】300萬人聯署反廣西狗肉節","createTime":"2018-06-07T05:22:36.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-08T03:10:39.000Z","uid":2054,"like":6,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"ef9b343ad2a5cf417999d7633188f8a052780e98","tid":692944,"uid":2054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-07T05:22:36.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180607/20413408\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180607%2F20413408&d=R949l7d43WBU2XNm%2FySWvZ7TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=138ccd46\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180607%2F20413408&h=f31a1d24\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180607/20413408</a><br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】今次研究所採用的樣本來自廣西的狗隻，不期然會令人聯想起當地進食狗肉的文化。於廣西玉林，每年6月都會舉辦「荔枝狗肉節」，據稱是當地的民間習俗；每一年的夏至，當地人就會大量食用荔枝與狗肉，BBC也曾經對此作出報道，於該活動中被宰的狗超過一萬隻。<br />\n<br />\n內地年殺1,000萬隻狗<br />\n<br />\n雖然有人稱，該活動是當地的民間風俗，但其實「荔枝狗肉節」的歷史並不悠久，最早只能上溯至90年代。《廣西日報》於2008年曾經報道，當年玉林市委、市政府實施四大「旅遊精品」工程，當中便包括了「荔枝狗肉節」。2009年時，玉林市旅遊局主辦了玉林國際旅遊美食節武林烹飪大賽，「玉林脆皮狗」於評選中更獲得美味金獎。<br />\n儘管飽受國內及國外輿論所炮轟，但當地的主辦單位似乎無意停辦「荔枝狗肉節」。<br />\n據報道，今年的「荔枝狗肉節」將會在本月21日舉行，全球各地的愛狗人士，早已經在各個平台發起聯署活動，<a href=\"http://其中在change.org\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E5%85%B6%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%A8change.org&d=R949l7d43WBU2XNm%2FySWvZ7TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=92f5155b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">其中在change.org</a>的平台已經錄得超過300萬人聯署，要求當地停止這個虐待狗隻的活動。<br />\n根據國際人道對待動物協會（Humane Society International）所作出的統計，每年在亞洲就有3,000萬隻狗被屠宰，當中約1,000萬隻是在中國被宰殺食用。"},{"pid":"46f0de836cf904121ab0473080c7b5efb721a8be","tid":692944,"uid":22553,"like":7,"dislike":2,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-07T05:24:20.000Z","msg":"愛狗撚全面進場<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd031c00cacc5d5bfd1ccfc813f18bfb2be164b7","tid":692944,"uid":14829,"like":9,"dislike":7,"score":2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-06-07T05:25:49.000Z","msg":"如果食狗肉可以好似豬羊雞牛咁樣發展到一套完善嘅養殖到宰殺系統，到時仲有冇人反對食狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b765cd4a706f2cbb16e160e0fda120a8f78de3e8","tid":692944,"uid":2054,"like":31,"dislike":1,"score":30,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-07T05:31:48.000Z","msg":"大家都愛狗，你們愛生的，老衲愛熟的"},{"pid":"c9eeeab2bb3ad1a7e124264cc3e91bb1875baf26","tid":692944,"uid":28563,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-07T05:32:26.000Z","msg":"留名睇平等撚支持食狗，雖然大陸班仆街係會偷人地養既狗，等睇連登仔支持果班人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ec9b1bec3cda7821267882e5bc439377baa0919","tid":692944,"uid":31841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-07T05:33:20.000Z","msg":"正呀,好肚餓<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3c2e42fa55b5b5c497d4f0f33df63189bd84096","tid":692944,"uid":49359,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-07T05:34:12.000Z","msg":"可以醜化支那就要利用"},{"pid":"691b0cf004ce76c6bbb2aba8b111852858045035","tid":692944,"uid":55488,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-07T05:34:22.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f858c22044d2e04ddc94d83643677265b81f38f2","tid":692944,"uid":6352,"like":6,"dislike":3,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-07T05:37:54.000Z","msg":"兩廣港澳本來就有食狗文化，廣東無得7788，反而廣西人有種，堅持保育本土文化，抵讚。"},{"pid":"7a461afe539b3f804b2e69aa0b11ec41276cb976","tid":692944,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b765cd4a706f2cbb16e160e0fda120a8f78de3e8","tid":692944,"uid":2054,"like":31,"dislike":1,"score":30,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-07T05:31:48.000Z","msg":"大家都愛狗，你們愛生的，老衲愛熟的"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"201